snippet.title: Somnium Tenebris - Investigative Co-Op Horror Game - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2875100/Somnium_Tenebris/
Somnium Tenebris is a 5-player, investigative horror game set in a Lovecraftian world. Explore the depths of the ocean with your team as you uncover evidence in your efforts to identify the megalithic creature... and escape before it's too late.

Coming in July 2024. Wishlist on Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2875100/Somnium_Tenebris/
